Ecology.Relationships:
[[File:Giant owl.png|thumb|273px|''A giant owl being used as a [[mount]].'']]
Giant owls could be trained to serve as mounts. They often served in this role with [[wood elves]], besides being their companions, because of their common vision of the world and nature.{{Cite dragon/269/Animal Henchmen|31-32}}

Trained giant owl could be found in the library of the [[Society of Stalwart Adventurers]] of [[Suzail]]. The librarian owl retrieved and put away [[book]]s alongside [[flying monkey]]s.
